  "upgrade_suggestion": "The 2022 Hollywood/UMe reissue (r25155592, D004064401) is a modern remaster on 180g and would be a sonic upgrade. The 2011 reissue (D000436501) is also available. Original first pressings like this one have collector value but the 2022 remaster is the better-sounding option.",
